ve-views-of-israel-and-little-confidence-in-netanyahu/</link><description>我们调查的大多数国家的大多数人都对以色列持负面看法，对总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡几乎没有信心。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jun 2026 02:08:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/06/04/most-people-across-36-countries-have-negative-views-of-israel-and-little-confidence-in-netanyahu/</guid></item><item><title>大多数新绿卡发给了已经居住在美国的移民</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/06/02/majority-of-new-green-cards-have-gone-to-immigrants-already-living-in-us/</link><description>特朗普政府的一份新备忘录可能要求已经在美国的绿卡申请者从国外申请，这可能每年影响数十万人。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jun 2026 02:37:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/06/02/majority-of-new-green-cards-have-gone-to-immigrants-already-living-in-us/</guid></item><item><title>美国人认为谁会赢得世界杯？</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/06/02/who-do-americans-think-is-going-to-win-the-world-cup/</link><description>大多数美国人表示，他们不太可能关注 2026 年世界杯，尽管移民比美国出生的成年人更有可能收看。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jun 2026 02:22:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/06/02/who-do-americans-think-is-going-to-win-the-world-cup/</guid></item><item><title>联邦机构 X 账户在特朗普第二个任期内的参与度远高于拜登任期内的参与度</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/06/01/federal-agency-x-accounts-are-getting-far-more-engagement-in-the-second-trump-term-than-under-biden/</link><description>在特朗普第二届政府中，联邦机构在 X 上的观众参与度比拜登政府最后一年高得多。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jun 2026 02:33:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/06/01/federal-agency-x-accounts-are-getting-far-more-engagement-in-the-second-trump-term-than-under-biden/</guid></item><item><title>社交媒体影响者在加州州长竞选中的作用</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/?prc_email_campaign=social-media-influencers-role-in-the-ca-gubernatorial-race</link><description>☀️周四快乐！简报是您了解新闻和信息世界的指南。在这里注册！在今天的电子邮件中： 🔥 特色故事 政治资金正在流向社交媒体影响者，包括加州州长竞选。像亿万富翁 Tom Steyer 这样的候选人正在向创作者付费，以在网上宣传他们的信息，最近的竞选财务披露显示 [...] 由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jun 2026 01:14:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/?prc_email_campaign=social-media-influencers-role-in-the-ca-gubernatorial-race</guid></item><item><title>美国人对避免气候变化最坏影响越来越悲观</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/science/2026/05/28/americans-are-increasingly-pessimistic-about-avoiding-the-worst-effects-of-climate-change/</link><description>大约十分之六的美国人表示，包括美国在内的世界各国在避免气候变化最严重的影响方面做得不够。这种日益增长的悲观情绪是由民主党推动的。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 May 2026 02:00:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/science/2026/05/28/americans-are-increasingly-pessimistic-about-avoiding-the-worst-effects-of-climate-change/</guid></item><item><title>在全球范围内，四分之一的新车销量是电动汽车或混合动力汽车</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/05/28/worldwide-a-quarter-of-new-car-sales-are-electric-vehicles-or-hybrids/</link><description>在 8 个国家，2025 年销售的所有新车中至少有一半是电动或混合动力汽车。美国仅达到 10%，远低于 25% 的全球平均水平。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 May 2026 01:45:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/05/28/worldwide-a-quarter-of-new-car-sales-are-electric-vehicles-or-hybrids/</guid></item></channel></rss>